snippet.title: Spirit City: Lofi Sessions - Back to School Update
snippet.description:
Free Update Available soon August 26th

We’re thrilled to announce a new free update for Spirit City: Lofi Sessions, packed with new content and quality of life improvements to enhance your cozy, productive experience. This update will bring lots of new room customization items, new spirits, new avatar activities, improvements to the to-do lists, a new music playlists, and more to our beloved game.

Available on Steam for PC
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2113850/Spirit_City_Lofi_Sessions/

Join our cozy community!
discord.gg/spiritcitylofi
https://www.instagram.com/spiritcitylofi/
https://x.com/wearemooncube
https://ko-fi.com/spiritcitylofi

Song: Vermilion Cliffs - Odem Medo
Label: Homework Radio
